metadata.name: Meet Garry Kasparov in real life
metadata.description:
The most exclusive NFT in this collection, the winning bidder will get the opportunity to meet the most famous chess player in the world at The Plaza Hotel in New York City. Join Garry Kasparov for dinner, followed by a private discussion of chess, strategy, and world affairs in a suite in the hotel.

Terms & Conditions: https://1kind.com/terms-conditions
